        </p>

        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">Common signs include:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
