            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Habit Formation</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">The more you use food to cope with stress, the stronger this neural pathway becomes. Eventually, reaching for food becomes automatic when stress appears.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

